{"id": "sos002", "name": "Cam_61St_702_11_26", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_gears", "Hurried Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Captain!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Big B, you guys good?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "A few of the men suffered minor injuries... Gary's left arm and lateral abdomen were shot. Logistics already sent him back to A.R.C.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Oh yea...?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Relax, Captain, he'll be fine. It's hard to face combat drones without getting scratched up a bit.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Hey, hey. If that were me it wouldn't have been that bleak. Must be a difference in talent?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Shut up, Jackal.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Picks up gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Don't get pissed, Miss Freeze, I'm just speaking the truth... Hey Bambi, what's next? We going back to report this or what?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Hey! Bambi?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Oh, sorry. I was thinking of something. Everyone's here, right? Let's confirm everyone's condition once more.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_03", "Creature Yelps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Bo Bo?\nOh, Lucy. Didn't notice you there... what's up?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Squad is set up and good to go. Ready to re-execute the mission to capture Colin Neumann Jr.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Alright. I've informed headquarters of our plan of action.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "What did HQ say?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "You mean about me letting the squad save citizens without their permission? Haha, of course I got chewed out...  \n... Even threatened to withdraw my position. Luckily Instructor Edwards helped smooth things out.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Ah, sorry. Shouldn't bring him up...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "No, that... I don't care anymore.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Oh, yea... Okay, then.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "What about you? Do you blame yourself? About Gary.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Yeah.\nYou... can you tell?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Each time a squad member falls into a bad spot, you always have the same reaction.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "I ordered it, after all. Everyone had to face those drones without enough time to prepare. This time, we were lucky. But one day, I'm gonna make the wrong decision...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Anyone who's in the exploration team might have to sacrifice their life for the mission at any time. Everyone was aware of that when they stepped into the forbidden areas.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "You're right. But if you just think of yourself it might affect whether those beside you live or die... Haha, maybe my next psychological evaluation won't be up to standard.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Picks up gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "image", "attrs": ["sos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy...? What is this...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Did you forget? \"You can shoot whenever you want.\" That's what you said.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "I trust your judgement, so I didn't pull the trigger. Perhaps one day you'll do something I can't forgive... \n... But for now, you're still everybody's captain.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "What about you? Would you believe the guy who rushes to the front of the squad no matter how dangerous the situation?\nI'm talking about you, Sagar.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_02", "Creature Yelps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "...... ?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Oh... it probably thinks you're attacking me. Don't worry about it, Bo Bo.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "... That's enough for now.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Puts gun away"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Listen, Eagle-01 is your squad. Everyone will follow your orders. If haven't been taken out, we ain't going down that easily... \nPlus, we ain't giving you a chance to go see your family.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Haha... You're really something.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_gears", "慌てた足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "隊長！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "ビッグB、そっちはどうだ？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "仲間が何人か軽傷を負った……\nGaryが左腕とわき腹に銃弾を食らったが、すでにA.R.C.に運ばれてる。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……そうか……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "大丈夫だって。安心しろよ、隊長。\n戦闘用ドローンと対峙して、無傷で帰れる方がおかしいんだ。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "ま、俺ならそんなひでーことにはなんねぇけどな。\nこれが才能の差ってやつだ。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "口を慎め、ジャッカル。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃を構える"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "まぁまぁ、そう怒んなって、氷の女王様？\n俺はただ事実を言っただけ……なあ、バンビ、次はどうすんだ？\n戻って報告か？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "おい！バンビ！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……あっ、あぁ……悪い。\n考え事をしてた。\n全員揃ったか？\nもう一度全員の状況を確認する。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_03", "生き物の鳴き声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……ポー？\nLucyか、気が付かなかった……なんだ？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "小隊の整備は終わった。\nColin Neumann Jr.の任務に戻る準備はできてる。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "わかった。\nこっちも本部への報告が終わったところだ。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "本部はなんて？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "今回勝手に市民の救助活動にあたったことについてか？\nはは、もちろんご立腹さ……立場をわきまえろって。\nEdwards隊長がかばってくれて助かった。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……悪い。\nあの人の名前は出すべきじゃなかったな……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "いや、あのことについては……もう気にしていない。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "そうか……ならいい。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Garyにことについて、隊長は自分を責めてる。\n違う？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……あぁ。\n……バレたか。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "まあ、隊員が危険にさらされるたび、同じような反応されれば。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "命令したのは俺だからな。\nみんなが何の準備もできていないことは分かってた。\nそれでも俺はドローンに立ち向かうよう命じた。\n今回は運がよかったんだ。\nでも、いつかもしかしたら俺の間違った判断が原因で……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "探査隊の人間は、任務のために命をかける覚悟がある。\nその覚悟の上で封鎖エリアに足を踏み入れてる。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "お前の言うとおりだ。\nそれでも、自分の命令がみんなの生死を左右すると思うと……はは、次のメンタル検査やばいかもな。\nひっかかるかも。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃を構える"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "image", "attrs": ["sos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy……？お前……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "忘れた？\n「撃ちたければいつでも撃て」って言ったのは誰？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "私はあんたを信じてる。\nだから引き金はひかない。\nいつか私が許せないようなことをあんたがした時は……\n……でも今はまだみんなの隊長だから。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "あんたは？\nどんな危険が待っていても、みんなの先頭に立ち続ける自分を信じられる？Sagar。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_02", "生き物の鳴き声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "あぁ……お前が俺に危害を加えるとでも思ったんだろ。\n大丈夫だ、ポー。なんでもない。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……じゃあ、そういうことで。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃をしまう"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "よく聞いて。\nEagle-01はあんたの隊。\nみんなあんたの号令に従う。\nあんたがその足で立ち続ける限り、私たちも簡単には死なない……あんたをそんな簡単に家族の元へは行かせない。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "はは……お前らしいな。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_gears", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "隊長！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "大 B，你們小組沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "有些弟兄受了輕傷……Gary 左臂和側腹中槍，後勤已經帶他回 A.R.C. 去了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……這樣嗎……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "放心，隊長，他會沒事的。對付戰鬥用無人機，本來就很難全身而退。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "嘿嘿，是我的話就不會這麼淒慘。這就是才能的差距吧？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "閉嘴，豺狼。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "別生氣啊，冰沙妹，我只是說出事實……喂斑比，接下來呢？要回去報告還是怎樣？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "喂！斑比？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……啊，抱歉，我在想事情。隊員們都到齊了吧？我們再確認一次大家的狀況。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_03", "生物叫聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……小啵？\n啊，Lucy，我沒察覺妳過來……怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "小隊整備完畢，已經可以重新執行追捕 Colin Neumann Jr. 的任務。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "好，我也和總部回報完行動計劃了。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "總部說了什麼？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "妳是說我擅自讓小隊來救援市民的事嗎？哈哈，當然是被唸了一頓……他們還威脅要撤我的職呢，還好有 Edwards 訓練官幫忙講話。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊，抱歉，我不該隨便提起他……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "不，那件事……我已經不在意了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "是嗎……那就好。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "倒是你，是在自責吧？Gary 的事。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……嗯。\n妳……看出來了？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "每次有隊員身陷險境，你的反應都是同一種模式。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "畢竟是我下令的，大家都在準備不足的情況下面對無人機的槍口。這次算運氣好，但也許有一天，我會做出錯誤的決定……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "加入探勘隊的人，隨時都可以為了任務獻上生命。大家都是有了覺悟才踏進封鎖區的。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "妳說的對。不過，只要想到自己可能左右大家的生死……哈哈，下次的心理評測危險了，會不會不合格啊？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "image", "attrs": ["sos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy……？妳這是……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你忘了嗎？「想要的話隨時可以開槍」，這可是你說的。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "我相信你的判斷，所以沒有扣下板機。也許有一天，你會做出讓我無法原諒的事……但現在，你仍然是大家的隊長。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "那你呢？會相信那個不管狀況多危險，永遠跑在隊伍最前頭的自己嗎，Sagar？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_02", "生物叫聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊……牠以為妳要攻擊我吧。\n沒事的，小啵。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……就到此為止吧。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "收槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "聽著，Eagle-01 是你的小隊，大家都會跟隨你的號令。你沒倒下，我們也不會輕易喪命……不會讓你有機會去和家屬見面的。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哈哈……真有妳的風格。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_gears", "다급한 발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "대장!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "B 형, 그쪽 팀 상황은?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "몇 동료들은 가벼운 부상인데.... Gary는 왼쪽 다리와 복부 측면에 총상을 입어서 이미 A.R.C.로 돌려보냈어.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......그랬군.....\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "안심해, 대장. 괜찮을 거야. 원래 드론 상대 임무는 몸 성히 돌아오기 힘들잖아.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "야야, 나는 아무리 퇴각한다 해도 그 정도까지 깨지진 않아. 임무가 다 똑같지 무슨! 그건 실력 차이지!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "입 닥쳐, 울프!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "총을 꺼낸다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "왜 또 성질부리시나~ 우리 얼음 공주님. 난 그냥 사실만 말했을 뿐이라고... 이봐, 밤비. 다음은? 돌아가서 보고할 거야 말 거야?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "야! 밤비!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......아, 미안하다. 생각 좀 하느라. 모두 도착했나? 우선 지금 상황을 다시 한번 확인하도록 한다.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_03", "동물 울음소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......보보?\n아, Lucy로군. 기척도 못 느꼈는데.... 무슨 일이지?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "소대원들 정비 끝났어. 곧바로 다시 Colin Neumann Jr. 추격 임무를 수행할 수 있을 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "알겠다. 나도 막 본부에 행동 계획 보고를 마친 참이야.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "본부에서는 뭐라는데?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "응? 아, 내 멋대로 팀원들을 동원해서 시민을 구한 일에 대해서? 하하하. 당연히 엄청 깨졌지...  그래도 Edwards 훈련관이 잘 말해준 모양이야.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아, 미안하다.\n나도 모르게 그 이름을...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "아니, 괜찮아.\n...이젠 아무렇지 않으니까.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "그래... 그럼 다행이고.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "너야말로 자책하고 있는 거 아니야?\nGary의 일.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......응.\n.....티가 나?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "항상 팀원이 위험한 상황에 처해질 때마다, 넌 반응이 한결같거든.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "어쨌든 내가 내린 명령으로 인해서, 모두들 준비도 안 된 상태에서 드론과 맞닥뜨리게 됐어. 이번엔 운이 좋았던 것뿐이야. 나중엔 내가 잘못된 결정을 내리게 될지도 모르지...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "탐사대를 지원한 사람들은 임무를 위해 언제든지 목숨을 바칠 준비가 되어있어. 그 정도 각오는 돼있어야 봉쇄구역에 발을 들일 수 있으니까.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "맞는 말이야. 그래도 모두의 생사가 자기 자신에게 달려있다고 생각하면.... 하하, 다음 심리 검사 때는 불합격 받는 건 아닌가 몰라.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "총을 겨눈다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "image", "attrs": ["sos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy......? 지금 뭐 하는...\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "잊었어?\n\"쏘고 싶다면 언제든지 방아쇠를 당겨\"\n네가 나한테 한 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "난 네 판단을 믿어. 그러니까 지금은 방아쇠를 당기지 않겠어. 언젠가 네가 용서받을 수 없는 짓을 했다는 생각이 들면 그때....하지만 지금은 아니야. 넌 여전히 우리들의 리더니까.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "자, 그럼 너는? 어떤 위험한 상황에서든, 영원히 팀원들보다 앞장서서 우리들을 이끌어 나가는 네 자신을 믿을 수 있겠어? Sagar?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_02", "동물 울음소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......? \n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "아......네가 나를 공격하는 줄로 착각했나 보군.\n괜찮아, 보보.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......오늘은 여기까지만 하지.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "총을 거둔다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "잘 들어. Eagle-01는 네가 이끄는 소대야.\n모두 너의 명령에 따를 준비가 되어 있어. 네가 무너지지만 않는다면, 우리들도 그렇게 쉽게 목숨을 잃거나 하진 않을 거야....\n절대로 네가 우리들 대신 가족들을 찾아가서 사과하는 일 없도록 할 테니까.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "하하하...정말 너다운 생각이군.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_gears", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "隊長！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "大 B，你們小組沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "有些弟兄受了輕傷……Gary 左臂和側腹中槍，後勤已經帶他回 A.R.C. 去了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……這樣嗎……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "放心，隊長，他會沒事的。對付戰鬥用無人機，本來就很難全身而退。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "嘿嘿，是我的話就不會這麼淒慘。這就是才能的差距吧？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "閉嘴，豺狼。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "別生氣啊，冰沙妹，我只是說出事實……喂斑比，接下來呢？要回去報告還是怎樣？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "喂！斑比？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……啊，抱歉，我在想事情。隊員們都到齊了吧？我們再確認一次大家的狀況。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_03", "生物叫聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……小啵？\n啊，Lucy，我沒察覺妳過來……怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": 