，Sagar？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_02", "生物叫聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊……牠以為妳要攻擊我吧。\n沒事的，小啵。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……就到此為止吧。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "收槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "聽著，Eagle-01 是你的小隊，大家都會跟隨你的號令。你沒倒下，我們也不會輕易喪命……不會讓你有機會去和家屬見面的。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哈哈……真有妳的風格。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_gears", "急促脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "队长！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "大 B，你们小组没事吧？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "有些弟兄受了轻伤……Gary 左臂和侧腹中枪，后勤已经带他回 A.R.C. 去了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……这样吗……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "放心，队长，他会没事的。对付战斗用无人机，本来就很难全身而退。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "嘿嘿，是我的话就不会这么凄惨。这就是才能的差距吧？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "闭嘴，豺狼。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "举枪"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "别生气啊，冰沙妹，我只是说出事实……喂斑比，接下来呢？要回去报告还是怎样？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "喂！斑比？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……啊，抱歉，我在想事情。队员们都到齐了吧？我们再确认一次大家的状况。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_03", "生物叫声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……小啵？\n啊，Lucy，我没察觉妳过来……怎么了？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "小队整备完毕，已经可以重新执行追捕 Colin Neumann Jr. 的任务。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "好，我也和总部回报完行动计划了。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "总部说了什么？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "妳是说我擅自让小队来救援市民的事吗？哈哈，当然是被念了一顿……他们还威胁要撤我的职呢，还好有 Edwards 训练官帮忙讲话。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊，抱歉，我不该随便提起他……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "不，那件事……我已经不在意了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "是吗……那就好。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "倒是你，是在自责吧？ Gary 的事。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……嗯。\n妳……看出来了？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "每次有队员身陷险境，你的反应都是同一种模式。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "毕竟是我下令的，大家都在准备不足的情况下面对无人机的枪口。这次算运气好，但也许有一天，我会做出错误的决定……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "加入探勘队的人，随时都可以为了任务献上生命。大家都是有了觉悟才踏进封锁区的。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "妳說的对。不过，只要想到自己可能左右大家的生死……哈哈，下次的心理评测危险了，会不会不合格啊？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "举枪"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "image", "attrs": ["sos0201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Lucy……？妳这是……\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "你忘了吗？ 「想要的话随时可以开枪」，这可是你说的。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "我相信你的判断，所以没有扣下板机。也许有一天，你会做出让我无法原谅的事……但现在，你仍然是大家的队长。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "那你呢？会相信那个不管状况多危险，永远跑在队伍最前头的自己吗，Sagar？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Po_02", "生物叫声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "啊……它以为妳要攻击我吧。\n没事的，小啵。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……就到此为止吧。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "收枪"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "听着，Eagle-01 是你的小队，大家都会跟随你的号令。你没倒下，我们也不会轻易丧命……不会让你有机会去和家属见面的。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哈哈……真有妳的风格。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}